(43, 6, 54, 50, 3, 7, 10, 'hath eternal life', 'Eternal Life and Knowing Christ', 'This connection highlights the theme of eternal life through a relationship with Christ. Both passages emphasize the importance of knowing Christ and participating in His sacrifice for salvation.', 'theme', 0.356, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
