(43, 6, 55, 43, 8, 31, 31, NULL, 'Connection of Discipleship and Sustenance', 'This connection highlights the importance of continuing in Jesus'' teachings as essential sustenance for spiritual life. Both passages emphasize the necessity of engaging with Jesus'' words and teachings to truly be His disciples.', 'theme', 0.34199999999999997, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(43, 6, 55, 19, 4, 7, 7, NULL, 'Connection of Sustenance and Joy', 'Both passages emphasize the theme of nourishment, with John 6:55 referring to Jesus'' flesh and blood as essential sustenance, while Psalms 4:7 speaks of gladness surpassing the abundance of corn and wine. This connection highlights the spiritual joy derived from divine sustenance.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'medium', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(43, 6, 55, 58, 8, 2, 2, 'my flesh is meat indeed', 'Connection of Sacrifice and Ministry', 'This connection highlights the theme of sacrificial offerings. Both passages emphasize the significance of flesh and blood in relation to divine service and the true sanctuary.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'medium', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
